com.ibm.team.workitem.client
Interface IAuditableClient

All Superinterfaces:
IAuditableCommon
public interface IAuditableClient
extends IAuditableCommon

Client specific part of the auditable library providing access to IAuditables. Can be obtained from ITeamRepository.getClientLibrary(Class) as a client library.

See ITeamRepository and IProcessClientService for additional documentation on operations that are forwarded to.

Since:
0.5
